tag_list: Nostalgic 90's "Television Remix" "Movie Remix" Funny
title: Nostalgia for The 90's Teen
description:
This isn't meant to be anything more than a funny "time capsule" for sound. I had the idea after finding a sound board filled with tiny clips from all sorts of shows and movies that I really liked, but knew my ten year younger sister would probably never see or know them. I kinda felt nostalgic in that moment, so I made this track to remind myself of my youth.
Try to guess all the quotes. Bet you can't!
